Cleanliness is next to godliness and nobody understands this more than instagram model Mihlali Ndamase. The famous Influencer claims that she is a neat freak and doesn't want to be around places that  are unhygienic and anybody who doesn't get this shouldn't set foot at her house. This the star revealed on her twitter account when she spoke out about how untidy spaces make her feel. "Untidy spaces irritate the living daylight out of me and if you don't understand that, or respect that, don't come to my house," she wrote. Since entering showbiz, Mihlali's name has grown  in a leaps and bounds. She is making serious money from being an charges as much as R25 000  for product or event placement on her Instagram account. She is ranked among Instagram's most richest influencers   